SYSTEM FLOW

1. User opens the website.

2. User uploads a policy or financial document 
   (PDF such as health insurance, mutual fund, or loan document).

3. Backend receives the uploaded file using Multer.

4. System validates file type and size 
   (only PDF/DOCX allowed).

5. Text is extracted from the document 
   using pdf-parse.

6. Extracted text is stored in MongoDB database.

7. System generates insights from the extracted text, such as:
   - Summary
   - Key exclusions
   - Important conditions
   - Charges or risks

8. System calculates a risk score 
   based on detected keywords.

9. Insights and summary are displayed on the dashboard.

10. User can start chat with the uploaded document.

11. User asks a question related to the document.

12. Question and document text are sent to AI.

13. AI generates an answer based on document content.

14. Answer is displayed to the user in chat format.
